{"tid":1648683,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"Trump既言行, 只係抄襲緊尼克遜既「狂人理論」, 無須大驚小怪","createTime":"2019-10-12T10:17:18.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-12T11:14:31.000Z","uid":235174,"like":8,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"74321477aff92ee636b976f0cb006f84dd4b5085","tid":1648683,"uid":235174,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-12T10:17:18.000Z","msg":"大家要了解一吓, Trump做緊既野同扮演既角色一D都唔新鮮同獨特, <br />\n佢都係抄襲緊之前既一個總統尼克遜, 而且一早理論化, 叫做Madman Theory, 係一種以扮演成喜怒無常, 令敵人難以觸摸既狂人作為談判策略, <br />\n我都係響Reddit度學返黎. 早起16世紀既「近代政治學之父」馬基雅維利已經提出過政治家要扮到癲癲地先有利於政治操縱, 所以一D都唔新鮮, 大家睇唔通先會咁驚, Trump知道貿易戰冇可能消滅中共除非用武力, 目的係要臣服佢, 同七擒七縱孟獲係一樣<br />\n睇吓呢度:<br />\n<a href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Madman_theory\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fen.wikipedia.org%2Fwiki%2FMadman_theory&d=Au6C6jYmoXJsWFOyr%2BboKOu9cyR3gY7uP1sO3WVLDIg%3D&h=bb63a151\" target=\"_blank\">https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Madman_theory</a>"},{"pid":"48094ad470635895a20852f5b567606570c4c13f","tid":1648683,"uid":307203,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-12T10:24:35.000Z","msg":"push<br />\n[品蔥建議] [拋磚引玉] 如何偽裝成一名合格的&ldquo;愛國港人&rdquo;（藍絲）？<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1648664\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1648664</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"cae6de9dc830b7db31a9cd76433782eefd509108","tid":1648683,"uid":193233,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-12T10:36:54.000Z","msg":"推！爭取選票？玩多中共4年？"},{"pid":"1ab1561210ada781494f3ffdd613511a70dbbead","tid":1648683,"uid":235174,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"cae6de9dc830b7db31a9cd76433782eefd509108","tid":1648683,"uid":193233,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-12T10:36:54.000Z","msg":"推！爭取選票？玩多中共4年？"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-12T11:13:39.000Z","msg":"從來都唔可以用言語黎衡量一個人既行為, 政客更加唔駛講, Trump更加唔可以"},{"pid":"da15373e2675c3b3cc5b517e60f08e444ce4539d","tid":1648683,"uid":279090,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"rep